## PREAMBLE

Before any competent national or international authority, before any notarial body, governmental institution, judicial entity, regulatory organization, or professional registry, I, **Lerry Alexander Elizondo Villalobos**, appear in full use of my civil, legal, and intellectual capacities to issue the present **Notarial Sworn Declaration**.

This document is structured in accordance with internationally accepted standards for sworn legal statements, ensuring clarity, verifiability, and public accountability.

